{"tid":896720,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【第24屆華鼎獎】周勵淇18年前齋睇《創世紀》 今憑《再創世紀》成最佳女演員","createTime":"2018-11-10T09:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T07:27:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"699022c53a6175da3e4f4f8be966a62caa934eb6","tid":896720,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"第24屆華鼎獎頒獎禮今日喺機場博覽館舉行，今晚入圍嘅電視劇當中，相信關注嘅係《延禧攻略》會唔會攞獎。賽前被一般人視為大熱嘅佘詩曼角逐「中國古代題材電視劇最佳女演員」，但佢缺席似有暗示。而行紅地毯時，台灣藝人張鈞甯未頒先知，自爆由青島趕落嚟攞「中國百強電視劇最佳女配角」。<br />\n周勵淇今晚先憑《再創世紀》贏到「中國當代題材電視劇最佳女演員」，佢話呢個獎特別有意義，佢話：「今年係入行18年，當年就係播《創世紀》，覺得感覺好微妙。自己好慶幸有份參與套劇，之前有睇過重播。今晚執行李慶祝，因為聽朝一早6點鐘，就要去北京做品牌活動。」<br />\n另外，陳家樂憑《東方華爾街》攞中國百強電視劇最佳新銳、黃景瑜憑《結愛&middot;千歲大人的初戀》贏中國當代題材電視劇最佳男演員獎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181109/large/1541766949_e5ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181109%2Flarge%2F1541766949_e5ca.jpg&h=fe50b429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181109/large/1541766950_7e03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181109%2Flarge%2F1541766950_7e03.jpg&h=21d03412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181109/58895152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181109%2F58895152&d=MT3PDYCEpOChyhPV5aSm9G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=900cd348\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181109%2F58895152&h=cb000e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181109/58895152</a>"},{"pid":"171459b20f8fac21ee7479065b41e81c986989c8","tid":896720,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得陳家樂好似kepa arrizabalaga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750590f35efaa9b3ad0eab12f362cbaeef0f7c8c","tid":896720,"uid":110018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"塊黃色布....好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4433a17a93832a739192cccc42ec07abb6b8fbd1","tid":896720,"uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"750590f35efaa9b3ad0eab12f362cbaeef0f7c8c","tid":896720,"uid":110018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"塊黃色布....好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"大陸d taste係咁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73d219b45f4212d46650671ca6cd8b94a86246b","tid":896720,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"攞曬d豬肉獎 tvb果個就唔好再出現啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b061b3ffb1b48d4e0b4c3874b87825f996f49a","tid":896720,"uid":110018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4433a17a93832a739192cccc42ec07abb6b8fbd1","tid":896720,"uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"750590f35efaa9b3ad0eab12f362cbaeef0f7c8c","tid":896720,"uid":110018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"塊黃色布....好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"大陸d taste係咁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔幾靚女都carry唔到呢啲taste<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}